cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on remote heart rate estimation from face videos, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the challenges of less-constrained scenarios and the need for large-scale databases, which are relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. Finally, the paper proposes a deep learning-based approach for heart rate estimation, which is related to neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) category.
